<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:16:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着市场升温对冲基金涌向日本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-funds-flock-japan-market-heats-up-2024-09-09/</link><description>日本在亚洲 4000 亿美元的对冲基金行业中脱颖而出，吸引了基金的推出，而其他地区却遭遇倒闭，这表明 8 月份的剧烈波动并未阻碍日本资本市场的复苏。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 08:25:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-funds-flock-japan-market-heats-up-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车销量连续第五个月下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-car-sales-fall-fifth-consecutive-month-2024-09-09/</link><description>周一的行业数据显示，中国 8 月份乘用车销量连续第五个月下降，尽管全电动和插电式混合动力车型的销量有所增长，这得益于对驾驶污染较严重的车辆的补贴。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 08:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-car-sales-fall-fifth-consecutive-month-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>网易发布即将到来的假期儿童游戏限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/netease-releases-gaming-limits-children-upcoming-holidays-2024-09-09/</link><description>网易游戏周一公布了在即将到来的中秋节和国庆假期期间中国儿童将被允许玩其视频游戏的具体日期和时段。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 08:13:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/netease-releases-gaming-limits-children-upcoming-holidays-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>读卖新闻报道，日本支持前外汇沙皇神田担任亚洲开发银行行长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-back-ex-fx-tsar-kanda-asian-development-bank-chief-yomiuri-reports-2024-09-09/</link><description>据《读卖新闻》周一报道，日本将支持前高级金融外交官神田正人作为下一任亚洲开发银行行长的候选人。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 07:47:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-back-ex-fx-tsar-kanda-asian-development-bank-chief-yomiuri-reports-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体称俄罗斯军队将于九月参加中国演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-military-join-chinese-exercise-september-says-chinese-state-media-2024-09-09/</link><description>据官方新华社周一报道，俄罗斯军方将派遣海军和空军参加中国九月份在日本海和鄂霍次克海举行的演习。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 07:36:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-military-join-chinese-exercise-september-says-chinese-state-media-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，随着贸易紧张局势加剧，中国八月份出口可能进一步放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-further-august-trade-tensions-mount-2024-09-09/</link><description>由于全球需求降温和贸易壁垒不断增加，中国这个世界第二大经济体的亮点可能会黯淡，因此八月份中国的出口增速可能为四个月来最慢。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 05:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-further-august-trade-tensions-mount-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>西班牙总理桑切斯访华，北京关注西班牙汽车和猪肉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/spanish-autos-pork-beijings-sights-with-pm-sanchez-china-2024-09-09/</link><description>西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯预计将于周一会见中国国家主席习近平，欧盟和中国正处于贸易战边缘，如果布鲁塞尔对西班牙电动汽车征收关税，北京准备对西班牙汽车和猪肉进行反击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 05:08:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/spanish-autos-pork-beijings-sights-with-pm-sanchez-china-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国仍忙于输出通货紧缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-09/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 04:33:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>韩国峰会制定在军事中使用人工智能的“蓝图”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-summit-target-blueprint-using-ai-military-2024-09-09/</link><description>韩国周一召开了一次国际峰会，寻求为军队中负责任地使用人工智能（AI）制定蓝图，不过预计任何协议都不会具有强制执行的约束力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 02:24:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-summit-target-blueprint-using-ai-military-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>明星交易撮合者缺席，华兴资本因交易恢复而暴跌，前景蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-renaissance-shares-plunge-after-17-month-suspension-former-chairmans-2024-09-09/</link><description>华兴资本因涉及这家精品投行前首席执行官和明星交易撮合者包凡的调查而结束了为期 17 个月的停牌，周一暴跌 72%，近期的损失令其前景承压。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 02:11:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-renaissance-shares-plunge-after-17-month-suspension-former-chairmans-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>8月中国居民消费价格上涨 PPI陷入通货紧缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-faster-pace-august-2024-09-09/</link><description>中国八月份的消费者通胀加速至半年来最快，但上涨的原因更多是由于天气干扰造成的食品成本上涨，而不是由于生产者价格通货紧缩恶化导致国内需求复苏。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:43:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-faster-pace-august-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国称与菲律宾的关系正处于南海问题的十字路口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-ties-with-philippines-crossroads-over-south-china-sea-2024-09-09/</link><description>在南海紧张局势之际，执政的共产党报纸《人民日报》周一发表评论，中国呼吁菲律宾“认真考虑处于十字路口”的两国关系的未来。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:23:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-ties-with-philippines-crossroads-over-south-china-sea-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>美元稳定，日元下滑，因交易员努力应对美联储降息前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-tentative-yen-dips-muddled-fed-rate-cut-outlook-2024-09-09/</link><description>美元周一收复部分失地，而日元回吐避险涨幅，因尚未决定美联储本月晚些时候预计降息规模的投资者正在关注本周的美国通胀数据以寻找更多线索。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-tentative-yen-dips-muddled-fed-rate-cut-outlook-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市下滑，但美国和欧盟期货找到买盘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-09/</link><description>由于对美国和中国经济增长的担忧打压市场情绪，亚洲股市周一下跌，尽管美国和欧洲股票期货确实实现了反弹，而债券收益率也脱离了低点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 00:25:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，中国国家主席习近平和俄罗斯总统普京向朝鲜领导人金正恩致以问候</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-russias-putin-send-greetings-north-koreas-kim-jong-un-kcna-says-2024-09-08/</link><description>官方媒体朝中社周一称，中国国家主席习近平和俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在朝鲜成立周年之际向朝鲜领导人金正恩致以问候。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 23:16:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-russias-putin-send-greetings-north-koreas-kim-jong-un-kcna-says-2024-09-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>